{"tid":2311611,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★保就業資助後---中國飛機服務：今日(4日)宣布裁員160人","createTime":"2020-12-04T08:07:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T10:38:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ee40e3a43c27aab49d188aabe69d658a142fce39","tid":2311611,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:07:08.000Z","msg":"在香港機場提供飛機維修服務的中國飛機服務有限公司（中飛），獲政府兩期保就業計劃5500萬港元工資補貼後，今日(4日)宣布裁減約160名員工，約佔全體員工的17%，為該公司年內第2次裁員，累計已裁減整體近3分之1的人手。另外，管理層減薪及員工自願無薪假至明年3月，全體員工明年凍薪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201204/bkn-20201204135243590-1204_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201204%2Fbkn-20201204135243590-1204_00822_001.html&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGNey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=f47bf10b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201204/bkn-20201204135243590-1204_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"6c48734df86dcaff157e9b913d84d6f0e7d5ffde","tid":2311611,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"打J服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6e6c5a6d75a58787e41fd0a33d67fc8ae7dda5","tid":2311611,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:08:28.000Z","msg":"怎樣打飛機jpg"},{"pid":"e554b500708e1ee59c2d47b758cd1039a47e871d","tid":2311611,"uid":121580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6c48734df86dcaff157e9b913d84d6f0e7d5ffde","tid":2311611,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"打J服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jab